Package: BINARY_PLACEHOLDER
Version: VERSION_PLACEHOLDER
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Mans <mans@example.com>
Description: configurable human-in-the-loop workflow runner for Claude Code
 ywflow wraps Claude Code sessions with a structured, config-driven workflow.
 Each step launches an interactive Claude Code session with the correct model,
 context, and skills pre-configured, keeping a human in control at each
 transition.
 .
 The workflow is defined in ywflow.yaml at the project root. All steps declared
 in that file are registered as subcommands at runtime; setup is the only
 built-in subcommand. Variable expansion is supported via ${var}, ${task}, and
 ${env:VAR} syntax.
